Improve Search Accuracy with Hybrid Search (Beta) 
Combine semantically aware vector search with keyword search to provide users the most relevant results. Hybrid search merges retrieved information from both searches and ranks results to show the most relevant information. You can influence search results by configuring ranking factors, such as record recency or popularity.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

NOTE: Hybrid Search in Data Cloud is a beta service subject to Beta Services Terms at Agreements - Salesforce.com or a written Unified Pilot Agreement if executed by Customer. Use of this beta service is at the Customer’s sole discretion but once enabled in beta, cannot be disabled.
